    scene bg ship_interior with dissolve
    narrator "{i}Forum threads. Incident reports. Bounty postings that had been claimed and closed. News articles from rim stations she'd never heard of. A surprisingly detailed wiki entry that someone kept updating with information they shouldn't have.{/i}"
