    narrator "{i}Later, alone in her bunk, Avyanna pulls up one more search.{/i}"
    narrator "{i}\"God Eye\" Vesper Rook{/i}"
    narrator "{i}The results are sparse-Vesper is better at controlling her own narrative. But there are fragments. Whispers. The occasional bounty hunter who claims to have seen her shoot a weapon out of someone's hand from two hundred meters.{/i}"
