    narrator "{i}\"She had a revolver. Old model. Custom grip. She never drew it. Never even touched it. But everyone in the room knew-if she wanted us dead, we'd be dead before we heard the shot. That's why they call her God Eye. She doesn't miss. She just chooses not to fire.\"{/i}"
